# AI Internship Agent - Comprehensive Review Report

> [!NOTE]
> This review covers the full edge-to-edge testing of the AI Internship Application Assistant. The test confirmed frontend-backend integration, API responsiveness, AI tool usage, and overall application health.

## 1. Project Overview & Setup Checkout
The application was successfully reviewed with the **backend** running on `http://localhost:5000` and **frontend** running on `http://localhost:3000`. We avoided destructive database setup, ensuring no core data was tampered with, directly linking the application to your existing PostgreSQL configuration. The `llama3` local model is also active and listening.

