## 2. Tested Features & Workflow

### 🚀 Landing & Authentication
- **Landing Page:** Minimalist, beautifully styled dashboard entry point.
- **Authentication:** Both Registration and Login flows work properly. User is successfully authenticated via JWT (short-lived access + refresh tokens).
  > [!TIP]
  > **Observation:** Currently, completing the registration successfully prompts the user to log in rather than auto-logging them into the dashboard.

### 📋 Dashboard & Resume Management
- **Dashboard Overview:** Accurately reflects Resumes, Applications, and AI Tool usage counters.
- **Resume Creation:** We successfully used the UI to create custom resumes. The backend APIs cleanly accepted the `POST /api/resumes` payload.

### 💼 Jobs & Applications
- **Job Discoverability:** Verified scrolling and pagination filters for jobs. Server-side search seamlessly integrates.
- **Apply Flow:** Submitting an application attaches the selected resume ID to the job. It behaves reliably with proper success notifications.
  
### 🧠 AI Toolkit
All tools interface with the backend `ai.controller.js` routes successfully.
- **Skill Parsing:** Extracting structured JSON from resume bodies is rapid and caches correctly.
- **Job Matching:** Yielded a 100% match score when given closely matching test data, correctly highlighting matched and missing skills.
- **Cover Letter Generation:** Initiated test, but encountered an issue (listed below in Bugs).

